'''BlackBerry 10'''，是由[[黑莓公司|黑莓公司]]所研發的[[行動作業系統|行動作業系統]]，使用於他們公司所開發的[[黑莓手機|黑莓手機]]之上<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.cgtn.com/news/3567444e7a6b7a6333566d54/index.html |title=BlackBerry must face revived US lawsuit over BlackBerry 10 |work=news.cgtn.com |accessdate=2021-12-29 |language=en |archive-date=2021-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229235804/https://news.cgtn.com/news/3567444e7a6b7a6333566d54/index.html }}</ref>。作為[[BlackBerry_OS|BlackBerry OS]]的後繼者，它以RIM公司在2010年所收購的作業系統核心[[QNX|QNX]]为内核打造，并融入了功能并不完整的[[安卓|安卓]][[虚拟机|虚拟机]]以丰富软件支持。<ref>{{cite news |title=Blackberry maker changes name, unveils new phones - People's Daily Online |url=http://en.people.cn/90778/8115343.html |accessdate=2021-12-29 |work=en.people.cn |archive-date=2021-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230004827/http://en.people.cn/90778/8115343.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://tech.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJy7rX |title=BlackBerry 10官网放出手机图片 将不局限于触屏版 |accessdate=2021-12-29 |archive-date=2021-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211229234647/https://tech.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJy7rX }}</ref>

==系统特点==
